Author: thekroganrebellions
Text: I feel this. For me it was anorexia restricting subtype---> recovery ---> relapse ----> anorexia binge/purge subtype.   I used to eat less than 300 calories a day and never binge but now, even when I high restrict, I still have binge/purge episodes once a week. R.I.P self control ðŸ˜¢.
